  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Cork</b> is a resource exclusive to the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC. It can be gathered by chopping down <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tree/Claw_Palm_Tree\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Tree/Claw Palm Tree\">Claw Palm Trees</a> and is required for several <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Crafting\" title=\"Crafting\">Crafting</a> recipes.\n</p><p>Cork can also be used to repair <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wood_Wall\" title=\"Wood Wall\">Wood Walls</a> and to refuel <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Candle_Hat\" title=\"Cork Candle Hat\">Cork Candle Hats</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork\" title=\"Cork\"><img alt=\"Cork.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork.png?15062a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Iron_Ore\" title=\"Iron Ore\"><img alt=\"Iron Ore.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Iron_Ore.png?8b281f\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Candle_Hat\" title=\"Cork Candle Hat\"><img alt=\"Cork Candle Hat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork_Candle_Hat.png?1d80e5\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork\" title=\"Cork\"><img alt=\"Cork.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork.png?15062a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>3</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Boards\" title=\"Boards\"><img alt=\"Boards.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Boards.png?79a528\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Science_Machine\" title=\"Science Machine\"><img alt=\"Science Machine.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Science_Machine.png/42px-Science_Machine.png?341685\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Bat\" title=\"Cork Bat\"><img alt=\"Cork Bat.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork_Bat.png?e7f345\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork\" title=\"Cork\"><img alt=\"Cork.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork.png?15062a\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>2</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Rope\" title=\"Rope\"><img alt=\"Rope.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Rope.png?41fbab\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><a href=\"http