</td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cork_Bowl_Canoe\" title=\"Cork Bowl Canoe\"><img alt=\"Cork Bowl Canoe.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork_Bowl_Canoe.png?514948\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Cork originally had red leaves, but the color was changed in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet#Version_History\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Quality of Life</a></i> update.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Gallery\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint\" title=\"Blueprint\"><img alt=\"Blueprint.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint.png/32px-Blueprint.png?80b6b5\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Gallery</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Cork_Old.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The old design of Cork.\"><img alt=\"The old design of Cork.\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Cork_Old.png?4394f9\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">The old design of Cork.</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
